                    "text": "1. Materially lower. The exemptions afforded under \u00a7 1026.43(d)(3) apply to a refinancing only if the monthly payment for the new loan is \u201cmaterially lower\u201d than the monthly payment for an existing non-standard mortgage. The payments to be compared must be calculated based on the requirements under \u00a7 1026.43(d)(5). Whether the new loan payment is \u201cmaterially lower\u201d than the non-standard mortgage payment depends on the facts and circumstances. In all cases, a payment reduction of 10 percent or more meets the \u201cmaterially lower\u201d standard."
                }
            }
